adept.common

Class ScriptEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • adept.common.ScriptEvent

  • public final class ScriptEvent
extends Object
    An event in a Script. The local data of this class is immutable so long as the IType used is, which is very likely, but the data inherited from HltContent and Item is mutable. The Object.hashCode() and Object.equals(Object) implementations are the default.
